# VEHICLE::SET_MISSION_TRAIN_AS_NO_LONGER_NEEDED

## Summary
Sets a mission train as no longer needed (must have been created by this script)

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX\*** train
* **INT** flags = 0

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
p1 is always 0
